@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = tu_access_token_aqui

### 1. Registrar 500ml de agua (Endpoint POST /api/water)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/water/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount_ml": 500
}

### 2. Consultar el progreso de hoy
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/water/progress/today
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Prueba de Seguridad (Sin auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/water/progress/today